	                                <h1 class="title"><img src="/sites/all/themes/redux/css/images/public_icon.png" alt="Visible to the public" title="Visible to the public" width="16" height="14" class="privacy-icon-public" />&nbsp;The Drupal CMS</h1>
                                                                        <ul id="service-menu" class="tabs service-menu"><li class="active" ><a href="/node/6742" class="active">View</a></li>
</ul>                                </div>
