			</td>
		</tr><tr><td>
				<p style="text-align:left;">Forum topic</p>
			</td>
			<td style="width:523px;">
				<p style="text-align:left;">A <em>forum topic</em> is the initial post to a new discussion thread within a forum.</p>
			</td>
		</tr><tr><td>
				<p style="text-align:left;">Group</p>
			</td>
